casebody.data:
KURTZ v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 32,

September Term, 1963.]

Decided February 14, 1964.

Before Brune, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott, Horney, Marbury and Sybert, JJ.

*607Per Curiam.

For the reasons assigned in Judge Oppenheimer’s opinion below, the application for leave to appeal will be denied.

Application denied.
